Name: Pylon Us3000c 74ah 48v 3.5kwh Lithium Ion Battery
description:
Pylon Us3000c 74ah 48v 3.5kwh Lithium Ion Battery is the new energy storage products developed and produced by Pylontech, it can be used to support reliable power for various types of equipment and systems. US3000C has built-in BMS battery management system, which can manage and monitor cells information including voltage, current and temperature.

Pylontech's US3000C lithium battery is a new version of the already well-known US3000. Capacity 3.55 kWh US3000C's simplicity and modularity make it suitable for small and large capacity storage systems that can scale to meet current and future energy demands.

Features

  • Build-in soft-start function able to reduce current strike when the inverter

  • NEW: Dual active protection on BMS level.

  • NEW: Automatic address setting when connect in multi-group.

  • Support wake-up by 5~12V signal from RJ45 port.

  • NEW: Enable 95% depth of discharge, available for the inverter which completely follows Pylontech latest protocol to operate.

  • The module is non-toxic, non-polluting, and environmentally friendly

  • Cathode material is made from LiFePO4 with safety performance and long cycle life

  • Battery management system (BMS)has protection functions including over-discharge, over-charge, over-current, and high/low temperature

  • The system can automatically manage the charge and discharge state and balance voltage of each cell

  • Flexible configuration, multiple battery modules can be in parallel for expanding capacity and power

  • Adopted self-cooling mode rapidly reduced system's entire noise

  • The module has less self-discharge, up to 6 months without charging it on the shelf, no memory effect, excellent performance of shallow charge and discharge

Specifications

Name: PYLON US2000 50AH 48V 2.4KWH LITHIUM IRON BATT
description:
US2000 series is an ideal solution for residential storage applications, with standard 48V/50AH specification, up to 95% usable capacity, and a 6,000 cycle-life warranty. Features
  • It is the ideal solar battery for homes and offices.
  • This Pylontech solar battery comes with up to 7 years of warranty and we have approved installers Zimbabwe wide
  • Pylontech us2000 has a life span of over 10 years and is very suitable for small and medium energy storage
Reminders
  • If the battery is stored for a long time, it is required to charge every six months and the
  • SOC should be no less than 90%.
  • The battery needs to be recharged within 12 hours after fully discharged.
  • Do not expose the cable outside.
  • All the battery terminals must be disconnected for maintenance.
  • Please contact the supplier within 24 hours if there is something abnormal.
  • Do not use cleaning solvents to clean the battery.
  • Do not expose the battery to flammable or harsh chemicals or vapors.
  • Do not paint any part of the battery, including any internal or external
  • The battery needs to be recharged within 12 hours after fully discharged.

Name: Pylontech UP2500 106AH 24V lithium battery
description:
Introducing the UP2500 Lithium-ion Phosphate Battery

The Pylontech UP2500 106AH 24V lithium-ion phosphate battery is a cutting-edge energy storage solution designed and manufactured by Pylontech.

Versatile Power for Various Applications

This innovative battery is engineered to provide reliable power support for a wide range of devices and systems, making it a versatile choice for many applications.

Ideal for Challenging Environments

The UP2500 battery is especially well-suited for environments with specific requirements, such as those with limited installation space, restricted load capacity, or the need for long-lasting performance.

Enhanced Battery Management

One of the standout features of the UP2500 is its integrated Battery Management System (BMS). The BMS actively monitors critical cell parameters, including voltage, current, and temperature.

Extending Battery Life

Additionally, the BMS plays a crucial role in balancing the charging and discharging of individual cells. This not only ensures optimal performance but also extends the overall service life of the battery.

A Trusted Choice in Zimbabwe

The UP2500 lithium-ion phosphate battery by Pylontech has gained significant popularity and trust among users in Zimbabwe. It is the go-to solution for fulfilling energy storage needs in the region. By incorporating subheadings, this revised content breaks down information into easily digestible sections, making it more reader-friendly and SEO-friendly.

Features

  • The whole module is non-toxic, non-polluting, and environmentally friendly.

  • The cathode material is made from LiFePO4 with safety performance and long cycle life.

  • Battery management system (BMS)has protection functions including over-discharge, overcharge, over-current, and high/low temperature.

  • The system can automatically manage the charge and discharge state and balance the current and voltage of each cell.

  • Flexible configuration, multiple battery modules can be in parallel for expanding capacity and power

  • Adopted self-cooling mode rapidly reduced system entire noise; The module has less self-discharge, up to 6 months without charging it on the shelf, no memory effect, and excellent performance of shallow charge and discharge.

  • The working temperature range is from -10℃ to 55℃, (Charging 0~55℃; discharging -10~55℃) with excellent discharge performance and cycle life.

  • Small size and lightweight, the standard 19-inch embedded module is comfortable for installation and maintenance.
